prop.name: providesService
prop.desc: The service provided by this channel.

prop.name: serviceLocation
prop.desc: The location (e.g. civic structure, local business, etc.) where a person can go to access the service.

prop.name: servicePostalAddress
prop.desc: The address for accessing the service by mail.

prop.name: availableLanguage
prop.desc: A language someone may use with or at the item, service or place. Please use one of the language codes from the IETF BCP 47 standard. See also inLanguage

prop.name: serviceSmsNumber
prop.desc: The number to access the service by text message.

prop.name: serviceUrl
prop.desc: The website to access the service.

prop.name: servicePhone
prop.desc: The phone number to use to access the service.

prop.name: processingTime
prop.desc: Estimated processing time for the service using this channel.
